The one with the red band is the oldest, Insoo. He's an 88-er. Then the 
singer with the short black hair (at 0:48) is second oldest and Leader 
Gunwoo, he's an 89-er. Then the black haired rapper is Seyong, a 91-er, and 
the blond rapper is Junkyu, a 93-er. And then maknae Chaejin is the singer 
at 1:03 with the white band on his head, he's a 95-er. =)  Hope that 
helps!!! They are seriously so good, their live stages are amazing!
